						<div class="postbody">I think the 3 frames : 1-&gt;2-&gt;1-&gt;3-&gt;1-&gt;2-&gt;1-&gt;.... sequences is what works best for walk cycles.
<br />Games with only 2 fames that constantly alternate (such as dragon warrior) have their charm too, this looks incredibly unrealistic but for some reason this just looks cool.</div>

					
